      <p>"You began this journey as an apprentice who did not know what a commit was. You crossed the foundations, mastered branches and merges, learned the ancient arts of stash and bisect. You forged automated pipelines in the great guilds. And now, you have <strong>walked beyond the walls</strong>."</p>
